<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - whạʿysẖ lk ḥty wlw krhwny ạlnạs
 whkwn lk ḥty wlw ạsmy byndạs
 1- ḥty wlw qạlwạ ʿny klạm ḥty wlw ṣạdfty ạlậm
 hạfḍl ṣạmd fyk ạ̉nạ mtmsk byk
 hạfḍl ṣạmd fyk yạ yswʿ ạ̉nạ mtmsk byk
 ykfy ḥyạty ạ̹n ạ̹nt mʿạyạ hrmy ạlʿạlm klh wrạyạ
 2- ḥty wlw nsywạ ạlkẖlạn ạ̹n ạ̉kẖwhm bʿdh kmạn
 hrmy bḥmly ʿlyk wạ̉ṣrkẖ wạ̉nạ bnạdyk
 hrmy bḥmly ʿlyk yạ yswʿ wạ̉ṣrkẖ wạ̉nạ bnạdyk
 ạ̹nt ạlkẖl ạlwfy dh kfạyẗ blqy fy ḥbk ly ḥmạyẗ
 3- gẖdr wmr wklh mnyn kẖạyf ạ̉qwlhạ ạ̹zạy kẖạynyn
 ʿlmny ạ̹zạy ạ̉sạmḥ wạ̉nsy ạlḥrf ạljạrḥ
 ʿlmny ạ̹zạy ạ̉sạmḥ yạ yswʿ wạ̉nsy ạlḥrf ạljạrḥ
 wạ̉fḍl nạẓr lyk qdạmy wfy ḥbk rạḥ ạ̉ʿysẖ ạ̉yạmy</lyrics>
<title>whạʿysẖ lk ḥty wlw krhwny ạlnạs</title>
